    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s been super well-loved and is in really solid shape, perfect for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. Let's get you behind the wheel and seeing if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2017 Shelby GT350 is a testament to high-revving atmospheric engineering, featuring the 5.2L Voodoo V8 with its characteristic flat-plane crankshaft and an 8,250 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise Tremec TR-3160 6-speed manual transmission, ensuring direct mechanical engagement. The chassis benefits from a MagneRide Damping System that provides exceptional transient response and roll control. This example maintains its factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential with a 3.73 final drive ratio and Brembo six-piston fixed front calipers for superior thermal management during aggressive deceleration. While the exterior reflects honest road use, the internal mechanical tolerances remain tight, and the oil cooling system has been meticulously monitored. A driver-focused machine optimized for high-lateral-G performance and acoustic purity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate pickup.",
