    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with practicality. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical marks of a car that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather seating is supple and intact, showing only light bolster wear on the driver's side. Every electronic feature, from the responsive touchscreen navigation to the dual-zone climate control and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in robust health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of all-season tires installed last season. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains quiet over bumps. If you are looking for a reliable, honest vehicle that looks great and drives even better, this is an excellent choice. Complete service records are available for your peace of mind.",
      "price": 33800.0,
